ing: 1 (12 ounce) container whipped topping (such as Cool WhipÂ®), thawed
1 (3.5 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
des: "This is so easy it is almost embarrassing! Nice light dessert that you make with a bought angel food cake."
ins: Whisk whipped topping, lemon yogurt, and vanilla pudding mix together in a bowl until frosting is smooth and thickened, 2 to 3 minutes. Spread frosting evenly on angel food cake and refrigerate until chilled, at least 30 minutes.
